== Docker image used for Github Actions CI

   The Github Actions CI uses a Docker image that is stored in the github
   cole-trapnell-lab docker repository. See github.com/cole-trapnell-lab
   'Packages' tab.

   There are notes for building, uploading, and linking the docker image
   to the monocle3 repository in the file

     URL: github.com/cole-trapnell-lab/Docker/monocle3_depend/NOTES

   The Dockerfile and supporting scripts are in

     github.com/cole-trapnell-lab/Docker/monocle3_depend/<monocle3_depend_version>


